[Princess Royal's Mansion]

13
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,390
Mother.

14
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,360
Mother.

15
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:04,040
I've already

16
00:02:04,110 --> 00:02:05,430
been lying here for several days.

17
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:07,590
I wish to go out and take a walk.

18
00:02:09,270 --> 00:02:10,430
Without my order,

19
00:02:11,390 --> 00:02:13,200
don't even think
of leaving Mingyue Pavilion.

20
00:02:13,830 --> 00:02:15,110
Even if I lie down here all day,

21
00:02:15,150 --> 00:02:17,110
it doesn't aid me in recovering.

22
00:02:17,590 --> 00:02:19,150
I've already sent out a statement.

23
00:02:19,829 --> 00:02:20,990
You're seriously wounded.

24
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:23,360
You're in a coma for a few days
due to your high fever.

25
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:26,829
Why?

26
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,390
Why?

27
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:32,920
Do you know

28
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:35,079
that the son
of the Chief Censor was killed

29
00:02:35,670 --> 00:02:37,710
besides Yang Shengcai and your cousin?

30
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,920
It's just the Chief Censor.

31
00:02:40,390 --> 00:02:41,360
What's there to fear?

32
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:44,590
Besides, Zhang Sheng

33
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:46,480
is a commoner's son
who wasn't favored by his father.

34
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:50,079
The Chief Censor is under Prince Qi.

35
00:02:50,550 --> 00:02:51,870
He's using this to his advantage.

36
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:53,760
He has already impeached you
in front of your uncle.

37
00:02:54,110 --> 00:02:55,110
Do you think your uncle

38
00:02:55,110 --> 00:02:56,240
can just stand idly by?

39
00:02:58,390 --> 00:03:00,520
The Capital Administration Office
has received an imperial order.

40
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,670
They're to investigate the case.

41
00:03:02,550 --> 00:03:03,430
You better stay

42
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,270
in Mingyue Pavilion

43
00:03:05,590 --> 00:03:07,360
without going anywhere
before the investigation is over.

44
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:10,800
Understood, Mother.

45
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,200
Do you have no idea

46
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:17,240
what started the fire?

47
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:21,960
I...

48
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:25,200
I was drunk.

49
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:27,800
I cannot remember.

50
00:03:32,270 --> 00:03:34,240
Since Prince Qi refuses to let it go,

51
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:38,240
I'll give him what he wants.

52
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,040
What are you guys doing?

53
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,200
Let go of my son!

54
00:03:41,590 --> 00:03:42,270
Mother!

55
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,360
Let go of my son!

56
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,430
What are you guys doing?

57
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:46,150
Let go of my son!

58
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,110
Let me go!

59
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:49,040
Sir, I'm begging you!

60
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:49,590
I'm begging you!

61
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:51,150
Sir, please let Chongyi go!

62
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,079
Madam.

63
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:54,390
Her Highness is inviting
your son to her mansion

64
00:03:54,550 --> 00:03:55,990
so that he can receive
treatment for his legs.

65
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,640
You guys are stopping us.

66
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,550
Do you intend to go
against the Princess Royal

67
00:03:59,990 --> 00:04:01,360
[Shijiu, Princess Royal's bodyguard]
and the Crown Prince?

68
00:04:01,870 --> 00:04:02,710
Do not think you can intimidate us

69
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:03,830
by saying so.

70
00:04:04,550 --> 00:04:05,390
This is Ling'an City.

71
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,480
This is the Duke of Anguo's Mansion.

72
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,430
Don't tell me

73
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:08,430
you wish to take him away by force.

74
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,830
Please thank Her Highness on my behalf.

75
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,830
Dear! Please rescue Chongyi!

76
00:04:13,830 --> 00:04:14,120
Father!

77
00:04:15,790 --> 00:04:17,829
My son is truly fortunate
to be able to receive treatment

78
00:04:18,589 --> 00:04:19,829
in the Princess Royal's Mansion.

79
00:04:20,829 --> 00:04:23,150
Father, what are you saying?

80
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,030
Sir! Chongyi!

81
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:28,120
Father!

82
00:04:28,150 --> 00:04:28,910
Chongyi!

83
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,120
Chongyi!

84
00:04:30,150 --> 00:04:30,640
Let me go!

85
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:32,200
Chongyi!

86
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:33,320
Chongyi!

87
00:04:34,150 --> 00:04:35,790
Dear!

88
00:04:35,790 --> 00:04:36,760
How could you let them

89
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,390
take your son away just like that?

90
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,830
Is your title as the duke

91
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:41,470
just for show?

92
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:43,640
That's right.

93
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,080
Are you happy now?

94
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,830
That's the Princess Royal.
She wields absolute authority.

95
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,230
She's backed
by the Crown Prince as well.

96
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:50,680
Do you think

97
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:52,030
a mere figurehead like me

98
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:53,590
can afford to offend them?

99
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,120
Will they do anything

100
00:04:55,150 --> 00:04:56,150
to my son?

101
00:04:56,790 --> 00:04:57,790
Tell me about it!

102
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,560
Each has its own destiny.

103
00:05:01,150 --> 00:05:04,270
That unfilial son
brought this upon himself.

104
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:09,230
Since it has come to this,

105
00:05:09,590 --> 00:05:10,560
I can't afford to sacrifice

106
00:05:10,910 --> 00:05:12,320
the entire mansion

107
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:19,440
and my unborn grandchild

108
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:21,120
just to save him.

109
00:05:23,710 --> 00:05:23,910
You!

110
00:05:25,790 --> 00:05:27,960
My son! Chongyi!

111
00:05:29,590 --> 00:05:30,350
Madam.

112
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,880
Her Highness has arrived!

113
00:05:58,909 --> 00:05:59,440
Are you the third son

114
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:01,440
of the Duke of Anguo?

115
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,590
Yes, Your Highness.

116
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:07,880
Your legs are injured.

117
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:09,200
Spare the formalities.

118
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:10,680
Get up.

119
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:12,230
Yes, Your Highness.

120
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,830
Do you know

121
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:16,830
why I brought you here?

122
00:06:20,350 --> 00:06:21,590
Your Highness,
thank you for your kind intentions.

123
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:25,910
However, my family is worried about me.

124
00:06:26,710 --> 00:06:28,640
It's inconvenient for me
to stay outside.

125
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,560
The house was on fire.

126
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,560
Only you and Mingyue survived.

127
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,909
The families of the three victims

128
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,760
must feel terrible.

129
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:42,080
The Cui family is under me.

130
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:44,520
The Yang family is on good terms
with me as well.

131
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,590
However, the Zhang family

132
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,230
refused to let us go.

133
00:06:49,909 --> 00:06:50,640
They insisted on

134
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,000
blaming their loss

135
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,760
on Mingyue.

136
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:57,350
Why do you think

137
00:06:57,470 --> 00:06:58,909
the Zhang family pestered us

138
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,960
instead of the Duke of Anguo's Mansion?

139
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:03,640
Your Highness!

140
00:07:05,590 --> 00:07:06,590
Your Highness, I respectfully request
your wise consideration.

141
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:09,560
That night, everyone was drunk.

142
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,150
I'm sure the wind

143
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:14,080
knocked over the candlestick

144
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,150
and started the fire!

145
00:07:16,030 --> 00:07:17,000
Both Princess Mingyue and I

146
00:07:18,150 --> 00:07:19,150
were victims!

147
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:22,150
The fire at the restaurant
was purely an accident!

148
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:24,790
Your Highness,
it was a natural disaster!

149
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,830
The Zhang family refused to accept

150
00:07:27,390 --> 00:07:28,710
that it was an accident.

151
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,200
Now, one of you two will be blamed.

152
00:07:31,910 --> 00:07:33,440
No matter if you knocked down
the candlestick

153
00:07:33,470 --> 00:07:34,470
and started the fire by accident

154
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:38,470
or committed arson after getting drunk,

155
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:42,880
the culprit cannot be Mingyue.

156
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:45,560
You're an intelligent man.

157
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,470
You should know what I'm talking about.

158
00:07:48,470 --> 00:07:49,909
Of course!

159
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,120
It can never be Princess Mingyue!

160
00:07:52,590 --> 00:07:53,520
It cannot be her!

161
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:58,640
No!

162
00:07:59,270 --> 00:07:59,830
No!

163
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,000
It wasn't me either, Your Highness!

164
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:02,680
Your Highness, it wasn't me!

165
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:04,230
It's...

166
00:08:06,230 --> 00:08:07,710
It's Jiang Zhan!

167
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:09,000
It's Jiang Zhan
from the Count of Dongping's Mansion!

168
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:10,960
Jiang Zhan?

169
00:08:13,790 --> 00:08:15,120
The Count of Dongping's Mansion?

170
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:20,000
Shijiu, check it out.

171
00:08:20,710 --> 00:08:21,710
Yes, Your Highness.

172
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:36,080
Poor Zhan.

173
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:39,350
He had already passed away
before he was able to get married.

174
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:42,230
Although the deceased is gone,

175
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:45,440
the living still needs to move on.

176
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:46,920
Mother,

177
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:49,830
shouldn't we decide

178
00:08:50,470 --> 00:08:52,440
on Zhan's funeral by now?

179
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:55,870
My brother hasn't been located yet.

180
00:08:56,230 --> 00:08:58,400
Nobody knows if he's dead or alive.

181
00:08:58,750 --> 00:08:59,470
But Aunt Xiao, it seems like

182
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:00,870
you're in a rush to hold his funeral.

183
00:09:01,350 --> 00:09:02,400
What ulterior motives do you have?

184
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,590
Zhan is gone!

185
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:04,990
I feel upset as well!

186
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,080
I know you two have a close bond.

187
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,350
You can't accept his passing.

188
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:11,710
But we've been searching
for him for seven days.

189
00:09:12,470 --> 00:09:15,080
There's no way he's still alive by now.

190
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:16,510
As the saying goes,

191
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,560
the dead should be laid to rest.

192
00:09:19,470 --> 00:09:20,200
Only then will we be able

193
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:22,110
to convey our grief

194
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,920
for Zhan's passing.

195
00:09:24,830 --> 00:09:25,870
No matter what,

196
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:28,630
I won't give up on the search.

197
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:33,920
Zhan is a poor boy.

198
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,750
We can't just let his soul

199
00:09:36,990 --> 00:09:38,200
wander around.

200
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:41,920
Let's hurry and plan for his funeral.

201
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,440
Yes, Mother.

202
00:09:43,870 --> 00:09:46,320
Both the Capital Administration Office
and our family

203
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,800
have conducted a search for days.

204
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,230
We only managed to find a shoe.

205
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:51,680
Most of the family's money
has been expended.

206
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:55,160
I'm afraid there's no hope.

207
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:57,800
Mother,

208
00:09:58,800 --> 00:09:59,990
I have something to report.

209
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:02,870
Lately, we've spent a lot of money

210
00:10:03,510 --> 00:10:04,750
to conduct the search for Zhan.

211
00:10:05,470 --> 00:10:06,870
The family doesn't have much money left.

212
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,200
If we intend to continue the search,

213
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,230
Mother,

214
00:10:10,830 --> 00:10:12,560
you need to allocate more money to us.

215
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,080
If he's alive, I need to see him.

216
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:17,680
If he's dead, I need to see his body.

217
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,510
We must find Zhan at all costs.

218
00:10:20,110 --> 00:10:21,080
As for the money,

219
00:10:21,870 --> 00:10:22,870
I'll think of something.

220
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,200
Anmou, you and your wife

221
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,230
don't need to worry about it.

222
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,630
Si, say no more.

223
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,320
Let's continue the search together.

224
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,560
It's all because you spoiled her!

225
00:10:32,830 --> 00:10:33,800
You spoiled her so much

226
00:10:34,230 --> 00:10:35,680
that she doesn't care
about anything in the world!

227
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:38,680
Your brother is dead because of you!

228
00:10:38,990 --> 00:10:39,560
Grandmother?

229
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:41,990
What are you saying?

230
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:44,320
Your brother is dead because of you!

231
00:10:44,990 --> 00:10:47,350
Ancheng, we've discussed

232
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,350
that Zhan

233
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:52,470
wouldn't stir up any trouble.

234
00:10:53,230 --> 00:10:55,590
We hoped that he could lead a posh life

235
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:58,560
and spend the rest of his life safely.

236
00:11:00,350 --> 00:11:01,110
But you?

237
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:04,160
You insisted on making him train.

238
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:05,750
He trained so much

239
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:07,160
that he didn't even have time

240
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:07,830
to have his meals!

241
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:13,400
Before this,
when Zhan left the house early,

242
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:16,320
he would come back in the evening

243
00:11:16,920 --> 00:11:18,440
and greet me.

244
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:19,750
But this time,

245
00:11:20,990 --> 00:11:21,680
he sneaked out

246
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:23,040
at night.

247
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:24,920
He didn't want to return home!

248
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:27,590
It's all because of you!

249
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:29,870
He died because of you!

250
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:34,800
It's all my fault.

251
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,320
I'm to blame.

252
00:11:36,470 --> 00:11:38,040
That's why I have to find him

253
00:11:38,110 --> 00:11:39,590
at all costs!

254
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:40,440
Si!

255
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:42,630
We're in trouble!

256
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:44,510
Old Madam, we're in trouble!

257
00:11:44,870 --> 00:11:45,960
There are troops outside!

258
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:47,630
They've surrounded our mansion!

259
00:11:48,990 --> 00:11:49,630
Let's go!

260
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:51,040
[Count of Dongping's Mansion]

261
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,280
Who are you guys?

262
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:56,080
I'm Shijiu, the leader

263
00:11:56,110 --> 00:11:57,400
of Princess Royal Rong Yang's bodyguard.

264
00:11:57,750 --> 00:11:58,630
I'm here to seal off

265
00:11:59,040 --> 00:12:00,560
the Count of Dongping's Mansion

266
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:01,440
under Her Highness's order.

267
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:02,870
Why is Her Highness

268
00:12:03,110 --> 00:12:04,680
sealing off our mansion?

269
00:12:04,830 --> 00:12:05,750
Regarding the arson case
at Huiyue Restaurant,

270
00:12:05,870 --> 00:12:07,080
Jiang Zhan is seen as a suspect.

271
00:12:07,230 --> 00:12:08,280
To prevent his escape,

272
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:10,710
Her Highness sent us here
to keep watch over the mansion.

273
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:11,320
Nonsense!

274
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:13,280
My brother has already been harmed.

275
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:14,920
Now, you want him to bear the blame?

276
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:16,200
We'll clarify everything with you

277
00:12:16,470 --> 00:12:17,680
once we find him.

278
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,440
We're doing this

279
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:20,040
for the sake
of your family's reputation.

280
00:12:20,630 --> 00:12:21,590
If you guys refuse to comply,

281
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,630
don't blame us for showing you no mercy.

282
00:12:24,710 --> 00:12:25,400
How dare you?

