After he saw me,

562
00:23:03,030 --> 00:23:04,360
he escaped by jumping into the water.

563
00:23:04,790 --> 00:23:06,160
But the restaurant was already on fire.

564
00:23:06,550 --> 00:23:07,550
It couldn't be extinguished.

565
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:08,790
Sir,

566
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,470
this man held a grudge against my family

567
00:23:10,750 --> 00:23:12,400
for canceling his marriage.

568
00:23:12,750 --> 00:23:13,680
His current statement is contradictory

569
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:14,710
and does not stand up

570
00:23:15,070 --> 00:23:15,750
to scrutiny.

571
00:23:16,030 --> 00:23:16,470
Sir,

572
00:23:17,550 --> 00:23:18,680
the burn marks on my legs

573
00:23:19,070 --> 00:23:20,510
are the most direct evidence I have.

574
00:23:20,790 --> 00:23:21,840
The situation that night was critical.

575
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:23,990
Everyone was panicking.

576
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:26,360
It's reasonable

577
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,750
if I couldn't remember the details.

578
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:30,360
Moreover, you have conducted
a search for days.

579
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:32,270
Jiang Zhan was the one
who was nowhere to be found.

580
00:23:33,030 --> 00:23:35,200
I'm sure
he must have fled to escape punishment.

581
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:39,030
Sir, please issue a wanted warrant
as soon as possible.

582
00:23:40,230 --> 00:23:40,960
Please uphold justice

583
00:23:41,470 --> 00:23:42,160
for the dead

584
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:44,230
and the wounded!

585
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:45,960
Your statements alone

586
00:23:46,360 --> 00:23:47,640
aren't sufficient to convict Jiang Zhan.

587
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:50,030
But right now,

588
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:51,750
we have to find Jiang Zhan

589
00:23:52,360 --> 00:23:53,750
before we can proceed with the case.

590
00:23:54,230 --> 00:23:56,310
Sir, my brother has told me everything

591
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:58,510
that happened on that night.

592
00:23:59,070 --> 00:24:00,680
Do you know where Jiang Zhan is?

593
00:24:01,230 --> 00:24:01,600
That's right.

594
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:02,920
Impossible.

595
00:24:03,790 --> 00:24:04,600
Isn't Jiang Zhan already...?

596
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:06,440
What did you say? Why is it impossible?

597
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:15,750
Indeed.

598
00:24:16,600 --> 00:24:18,200
The Count of Dongping's Mansion
deceived the public

599
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:19,600
by saying that Jiang Zhan went missing
after falling into the water.

600
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:21,230
In reality, you are keeping him
somewhere else.

601
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:23,840
Sir, you mustn't show favoritism!

602
00:24:24,400 --> 00:24:24,750
Jiang Si.

603
00:24:25,270 --> 00:24:27,200
Where exactly is Jiang Zhan?

604
00:24:27,750 --> 00:24:29,230
My brother appeared
in my dream last night.

605
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:31,160
He told me the entire story

606
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:33,070
without omitting a single detail.

607
00:24:33,550 --> 00:24:35,030
He didn't set
the pavilion on fire at all.

608
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:35,960
I can't allow any crooks

609
00:24:35,960 --> 00:24:37,120
to slander him.

610
00:24:39,510 --> 00:24:41,550
Thunder in broad daylight?
I'm sure there are grievances involved.

611
00:24:41,790 --> 00:24:43,360
I never expected Jiang Zhan
to appear in his sister's dream

612
00:24:43,470 --> 00:24:44,470
even after death.

613
00:24:44,600 --> 00:24:45,160
Do ghosts actually

614
00:24:45,550 --> 00:24:46,840
appear in one's dream
to relay their messages?

615
00:24:47,310 --> 00:24:48,510
Zhang Sheng lured my brother

616
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:49,750
to Huiyue Restaurant.

617
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:50,920
During that period,

618
00:24:51,030 --> 00:24:52,710
the five of them abused him.

619
00:24:53,120 --> 00:24:54,310
They abused him until he died.

620
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:01,120
Are they inhumane?

621
00:25:01,120 --> 00:25:01,360
That's going too far！

622
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:02,640
That princess is so cruel.

623
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:03,360
Precisely.

624
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:08,310
What a joke.

625
00:25:08,790 --> 00:25:09,880
We're in court.

626
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:10,790
How could we believe something

627
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:12,510
as ridiculous as a ghost
appearing in her dream?

628
00:25:12,840 --> 00:25:14,510
Sir, you may instruct your men
to conduct an investigation.

629
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:15,880
Among the evidence

630
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:16,600
that you guys have found,

631
00:25:16,790 --> 00:25:18,470
have you guys found
a duck-shaped incense furnace?

632
00:25:19,840 --> 00:25:20,160
Someone!

633
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:21,440
Make haste.

634
00:25:38,710 --> 00:25:39,120
Ji Chongyi.

635
00:25:40,030 --> 00:25:40,710
Let me ask you this.

636
00:25:41,470 --> 00:25:42,070
Did you see

637
00:25:42,600 --> 00:25:43,790
this furnace when you were there?

638
00:25:44,360 --> 00:25:44,550
I...

639
