I couldn't remember.

640
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,710
Let me help you
recall your memories, then.

641
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:51,230
When you guys got tired
of beating my brother up,

642
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,200
you realized that he
was no longer breathing.

643
00:25:53,750 --> 00:25:54,750
You and Cui Yi

644
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:56,510
dumped my brother's body
into the Jinshui River!

645
00:25:57,440 --> 00:25:58,160
Ji Chongyi!

646
00:25:58,990 --> 00:26:00,230
You murdered my brother.

647
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:01,960
You should pay for it with your life!

648
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:03,400
Nonsense!

649
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,230
I didn't kill him!

650
00:26:04,360 --> 00:26:05,470
I merely kicked him!

651
00:26:05,790 --> 00:26:06,840
Her Highness told the others

652
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:08,400
to push him into the river!
It's none of my business!

653
00:26:08,470 --> 00:26:09,400
I didn't kill him!

654
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:10,710
I didn't!

655
00:26:11,030 --> 00:26:12,600
Ji Chongyi, how dare you?

656
00:26:13,230 --> 00:26:14,360
How dare you malign Her Highness?

657
00:26:14,710 --> 00:26:15,960
Did he actually malign her?

658
00:26:16,270 --> 00:26:18,510
Or was the Princess Royal's Mansion
taking innocent lives for fun

659
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:19,680
just because of their authority?

660
00:26:20,360 --> 00:26:20,960
Do you guys think

661
00:26:20,960 --> 00:26:22,510
you can disregard the lives
of other people

662
00:26:22,840 --> 00:26:24,310
just because you all
are from the imperial family?

663
00:26:25,030 --> 00:26:25,920
Not only have you guys
committed a crime,

664
00:26:26,160 --> 00:26:27,070
but you guys also shamelessly

665
00:26:27,070 --> 00:26:27,680
shifted the blame

666
00:26:27,710 --> 00:26:28,880
onto an innocent person!

667
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:29,680
Precisely!

668
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:31,070
How could they bully them like that?

669
00:26:31,310 --> 00:26:32,510
They have no regard
for other people's lives!

670
00:26:32,510 --> 00:26:33,400
He's from the Princess Royal's Mansion!

671
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:34,440
Yeah! He is!

672
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:35,510
Mind your manners!

673
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:36,960
Silence!

674
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:39,070
This is the main hall
of the Capital Administration Office.

675
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:40,310
This isn't the marketplace.

676
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:43,200
Though dream communication
is improbable,

677
00:26:43,510 --> 00:26:44,640
Jiang Si's evidence

678
00:26:45,510 --> 00:26:46,550
precisely

679
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:48,990
matches the case.

680
00:26:49,600 --> 00:26:50,070
Let me ask you this.

681
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:52,880
Has your brother mentioned the fire

682
00:26:52,990 --> 00:26:53,960
when he was in your dream?

683
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:54,230
I...

684
00:26:57,750 --> 00:26:58,310
Remember.

685
00:26:58,510 --> 00:26:59,640
Tonight, you were with me all the time.

686
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:00,680
You didn't go anywhere else.

687
00:27:04,360 --> 00:27:05,880
The fire occurred because the wind
knocked down the candlestick.

688
00:27:06,270 --> 00:27:06,990
It was an accident.

689
00:27:08,120 --> 00:27:08,640
It's on fire!

690
00:27:08,710 --> 00:27:09,550
The place is burning!

691
00:27:09,750 --> 00:27:10,960
Stop drinking!

692
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:11,600
It's on fire!

693
00:27:12,120 --> 00:27:12,840
Hurry and run!

694
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:13,960
Fire!

695
00:27:14,120 --> 00:27:14,680
It's burning up!

696
00:27:15,070 --> 00:27:16,070
Fire!

697
00:27:20,360 --> 00:27:21,070
It's burning up!

698
00:27:21,230 --> 00:27:22,960
Why did they not act
when there was a fire?

699
00:27:23,310 --> 00:27:24,750
It's all because they were drunk.

700
00:27:25,070 --> 00:27:26,270
They thought the fire
was their hallucination.

701
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:28,640
After that, Cui Mingyue
was the first to escape.

702
00:27:28,840 --> 00:27:30,310
She jumped out of the window
and into the river.

703
00:27:31,600 --> 00:27:32,470
Zhang Sheng and Cui Yi

704
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:33,990
were trapped by the pillar.

705
00:27:35,710 --> 00:27:37,310
Yang Shengcai couldn't swim.

706
00:27:37,600 --> 00:27:38,400
He drowned.

707
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:46,160
Zhang Sheng asked Ji Chongyi for help.

708
00:27:46,710 --> 00:27:47,790
But he ignored his plea

709
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:48,640
and escaped alone.

710
00:27:49,070 --> 00:27:49,790
As for the two who were trapped,

711
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:51,030
they perished in the fire.

712
00:27:56,230 --> 00:27:57,790
Someone, summon the coroner.

713
00:28:00,790 --> 00:28:01,230
Sir,

714
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:02,440
Zhang Sheng's stomach does contain

715
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:03,710
a large amount of liquor
that was burned up.

716
00:28:03,960 --> 00:28:05,510
The Yang family and the Cui family

717
00:28:05,600 --> 00:28:06,710
didn't allow us to perform an autopsy.

718
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:08,230
Therefore, I don't know.

719
00:28:08,550 --> 00:28:09,880
But Zhang Sheng and Cui Yi

720
00:28:09,990 --> 00:28:11,790
did die from inhaling excess smoke.

721
00:28:12,230 --> 00:28:14,440
Yang Shengcai drowned.

722
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:15,840
All of her statements
match the coroner's!

723
00:28:16,230 --> 00:28:17,230
This is truly magical.

724
00:28:17,600 --> 00:28:19,270
I'm sure Jiang Zhan
suffered a wrongful death.

725
00:28:19,470 --> 00:28:20,470
His soul witnessed the entire process.

726
00:28:20,710 --> 00:28:22,200
That's why he relayed
the message to Miss Si.

727
00:28:23,550 --> 00:28:23,990
Ji Chongyi,

728
00:28:24,750 --> 00:28:25,750
it has already come to this.

729
00:28:26,070 --> 00:28:26,920
You better confess.

730
00:28:27,550 --> 00:28:29,600
Did you and the gang
conspire to kill Jiang Zhan?

731
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:31,270
Dream communication?

732
00:28:31,840 --> 00:28:33,270
This place shouldn't be called
the Capital Administration Office,

733
00:28:33,600 --> 00:28:34,600
but the Office
of the Underworld's Judge.

734
00:28:35,270 --> 00:28:36,440
We don't need magistrates like you all.

735
00:28:37,230 --> 00:28:38,550
Wouldn't it be easier
to just hire a psychic

736
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:39,400
to talk to ghosts?

737
00:28:39,840 --> 00:28:40,230
That's right.

738
00:28:40,750 --> 00:28:41,600
That's right.

739
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:43,070
What nonsense are you talking about?

740
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:44,310
I think something's off

741
00:28:44,310 --> 00:28:45,160
with the Capital Administration Office.

742
00:28:45,710 --> 00:28:47,470
You guys conspired with Jiang Si

743
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:49,270
and conjured such a tale
to deceive the public.

744
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:52,640
If you don't believe
in the existence of relentless souls,

745
00:28:53,360 --> 00:28:54,680
why did you confess

746
00:28:55,030 --> 00:28:56,920
that someone else abused
and killed Jiang Zhan?

747
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:59,200
Why did you say
that Cui Mingyue instructed them

748
00:28:59,270 --> 00:29:01,030
to toss Jiang Zhan
into the Jinshui River

749
00:29:01,070 --> 00:29:02,360
while you merely kicked him a few times?

750
00:29:04,270 --> 00:29:04,990
Just now,

751
00:29:04,990 --> 00:29:07,120
Jiang Si spooked me with her words.

752
00:29:07,470 --> 00:29:09,750
That's why I spoke without thinking.

753
00:29:09,790 --> 00:29:10,710
Is that so?

754
00:29:10,960 --> 00:29:12,640
Ji Chongyi, this is the court.

755
00:29:12,990 --> 00:29:13,960
Every single word and action of yours

756
00:29:14,030 --> 00:29:15,070
will be recorded.

757
00:29:15,840 --> 00:29:16,960
You won't get to deny it.

758
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:19,200
Anyway, I'm not convinced
that you can close this case

759
00:29:19,230 --> 00:29:20,550
with the statements
of dream communication.

760
00:29:21,030 --> 00:29:22,120
I'll never yield

761
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:23,270
unless you have substantial evidence!

762
00:29:23,310 --> 00:29:24,120
How dare you not yield?

763
00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:28,160
Who said he didn't have
substantial evidence?

764
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:43,710
Where did he come from?

765
00:29:43,990 --> 00:29:45,550
He's utterly drenched.

766
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:46,680
But it didn't rain.

767
00:29:46,750 --> 00:29:47,270
Indeed.

768
00:30:07,710 --> 00:30:09,070
A ghost!

769
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:10,070
That's a ghost!

770
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:12,960
A ghost!

771
00:30:17,120 --> 00:30:18,070
Ji Chongyi,

772
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:20,070
if you don't tell them the truth,

773
00:30:20,550 --> 00:30:21,120
I'll drag you down

774
00:30:21,200 --> 00:30:22,680
to the Underground with me.

775
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:24,990
Don't come near me!

776
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,440
I didn't kill you!

777
00:30:26,510 --> 00:30:27,790
It has nothing to do with me!

778
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:28,550
It's all...

779
00:30:28,840 --> 00:30:29,960
It's all because of Princess Mingyue!

780
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:31,510
She told me to do it!

781
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:32,120
The Princess Royal.

782
00:30:32,270 --> 00:30:32,920
She didn't want her daughter

783
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:34,400
to be involved with a court case!

784
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:37,270
That's why she forced me
to give false testimony!

785
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:38,230
Princess Mingyue

786
00:30:38,360 --> 00:30:39,310
didn't faint at all!

787
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,640
Go and find her! Don't come to me!

788
00:30:41,270 --> 00:30:42,710
I don't know anything!

789
00:30:42,750 --> 00:30:43,960
I didn't do anything!

790
00:30:44,550 --> 00:30:45,120
I'm begging you!

791
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:46,230
Please don't kill me!

792
00:30:46,230 --> 00:30:47,230
I beg of you!

793
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,200
Don't kill me!

794
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:55,310
Zhan.

795
00:31:05,510 --> 00:31:06,160
You're back.

796
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:09,400
Was the second son of the Jiang family

797
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:11,640
a soul? Or was he alive?

798
00:31:12,600 --> 00:31:14,790
The Capital Administration Office
can conduct trials for humans,

799
00:31:14,990 --> 00:31:16,400
but can they conduct trials

800
00:31:16,510 --> 00:31:18,120
for vengeful souls?

801
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:19,880
That's too much of a cliffhanger.

802
00:31:20,510 --> 00:31:21,790
Now, we have no mood to eat!

803
00:31:22,120 --> 00:31:23,160
- Precisely.
- Yeah.

804
00:31:23,360 --> 00:31:23,960
What about this?

805
00:31:24,270 --> 00:31:25,920
I'll pay you
for the next session as well.

806
00:31:25,990 --> 00:31:26,920
Tell us the entire story.

807
00:31:27,120 --> 00:31:29,600
- Yeah, hurry up.
- Yeah.

808
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:30,550
Hurry up.

809
00:31:30,600 --> 00:31:31,990
If you wish to know what happens next,

810
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:35,790
please attend the next session.

