00:32:00,600 --> 00:32:00,990
Father?

813
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:05,640
Father!

814
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:13,070
Zhan?

815
00:32:16,030 --> 00:32:16,310
Zhan!

816
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,070
Zhan!

817
00:32:20,510 --> 00:32:21,600
Zhan!

818
00:32:21,710 --> 00:32:22,070
Father!

819
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:23,790
Zhan, is it truly you?

820
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:25,470
I'm back.

821
00:32:26,990 --> 00:32:27,880
I'm glad that you're back.

822
00:32:29,440 --> 00:32:31,680
Zhan, I'm so glad!

823
00:32:31,990 --> 00:32:32,550
Father!

824
00:32:46,790 --> 00:32:47,710
Zhan, slow down.

825
00:32:47,750 --> 00:32:48,400
Don't choke yourself.

826
00:32:48,510 --> 00:32:48,920
This is so delicious.

827
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:49,790
Have some water.

828
00:32:53,230 --> 00:32:53,840
By the way, Zhan,

829
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:55,470
how are your injuries

830
00:32:55,790 --> 00:32:56,790
now?

831
00:32:57,160 --> 00:32:57,680
Yeah.

832
00:32:58,960 --> 00:33:00,680
Shouldn't we hire a physician

833
00:33:00,710 --> 00:33:02,160
