just in case?

834
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:02,960
I think so.

835
00:33:03,160 --> 00:33:04,960
No need for that. I've fully recovered.

836
00:33:06,360 --> 00:33:06,750
Look.

837
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:13,030
I'll return to my normal state

838
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,470
